[L. A. No. 10778. In Bank. November 10, 1928.] THE PEOPLE, Respondent, v. W. P. HODGES et al.. Defendants; SEABOARD SURETY CORPORATION OF AMERICA, Appellant.

*788Arthur T. Stollmack for Appellant.

EVerett W. Matoon, County Counsel, and S. V. 0. Prichard, Deputy County Counsel, for Respondent.

THE' COURT.

This case does not materially differ from People v. Hodges (L. A. 10777), ante, p. 476 [271 Pac. 897], and upon the authority of that ease the purported appeal herein must be dismissed.

The appeal is dismissed.
